{"tid":602815,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【派錢4千】張建宗讚派錢可取 望為預算案爭議劃上句號","createTime":"2018-03-23T08:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T09:12:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af9b5b4f03afda3f1712676a7ef3f4e759be1d41","tid":602815,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180323/large/1521792919_4c89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F1521792919_4c89.jpg&h=c4d26fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波公佈預算案的補漏拾遺措施，預計有280萬名市民將獲派發4,000元現金補貼。政務司司長張建宗回應指當局今次表現出「聆聽政府」的一面，因聽取了坊間的意見後而作出的「關愛和分享」的考慮，並決定聽從意見不透過關愛基金派發，認為派4,000元計劃是可取的方案，希望可為預算案爭議劃上句號。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，派錢計劃仍要要多作討論，包括計劃涉及多少行政費等問題，均要視乎實際財政狀況後再向立法會交代。他認為改由在職家庭津貼辦事處處理派發4,000元屬恰當安排，認為反映現時香港並非因貧窮問題而派錢，而是在考慮到關愛和分享經濟成果後才定出。<br />\n<br />\n今次4,000元補漏拾遺措施規定了受惠市民，必須為在2018年12月31日前年滿18歲、持有香港身份證、通常居港，而且為無交稅、無持有物業、無領取綜援或其他援助金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180323/57985392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57985392&d=hNXgKv16K%2FAoYbsNLvoNVbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=a67cce91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57985392&h=6307c9f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180323/57985392</a>"},{"pid":"48c7a0fbcc15905f40b0c347b42292115e894043","tid":602815,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一事無成張，轉態快如畫</span></span>"},{"pid":"38eaa9d947826fa442fafd47f8b79f778c3acca0","tid":602815,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:46:12.000Z","m